     <td align="center" width="120" bgcolor="#dddddd"><font class="GraphicCaption">"Scheduled downtime?  Sweet!  Although I'll have to have my eyes surgically closed to get some sleep."</font></td>
     <td bgcolor="#ffffff"><img src="images/spacer.gif"></td>
